Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.54,0:00:02.07,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can you...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.07,0:00:04.75,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,be friends with me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.95,0:00:06.50,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Friends?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.51,0:00:09.25,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.80,0:00:10.97,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.92,0:00:12.87,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.93,0:00:34.85,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome back, Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.85,0:00:35.74,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Did you have fun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.03,0:00:39.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, it was a lot of{was: really} fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.01,0:00:42.68,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,Don't force yourself, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.95,0:00:43.85,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,And...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.85,0:00:46.17,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,And I shouldn't get in too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:46.43,0:00:48.08,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I shouldn't let myself get in too deep.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.29,0:00:54.80,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Himura-san, would it be bad if I told someone about myself?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.80,0:00:58.78,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,If it's something you've decided, I won't object.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.78,0:01:00.89,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,As for my personal opinion,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.22,0:01:02.52,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,I don't approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.85,0:01:05.52,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.27,0:01:08.78,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I get into trouble,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.78,0:01:11.02,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I won't be able to regret it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.42,0:02:00.97,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,All right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.97,0:02:03.28,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, it's morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.70,0:02:07.54,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Wake up, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.41,0:02:13.75,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,If you don't wake up, you're going to be late.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.59,0:02:21.69,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Well then, since I've already gone this far,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.69,0:02:25.04,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,whatever happens afterwards is your own problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.60,0:02:31.81,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I told you to wake up!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.31,0:02:34.91,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.91,0:02:37.31,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't your methods of waking me up getting more and more violent?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.31,0:02:40.25,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Because you're sleeping in later and later.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.25,0:02:43.96,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Since it's bad for your health, didn't I tell you to stop sleeping at your desk?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.96,0:02:47.33,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be helped. Because the deadline is soon, it's a major crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.33,0:02:49.66,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't you say it's a crisis every single month?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.66,0:02:53.46,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Work is fine, but your real occupation is being a student.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.46,0:02:55.96,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Being a manga artist is also my occupation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.96,0:02:59.29,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Quit quibbling, and go wash your face right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.29,0:03:01.83,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, everyone will find out about your job.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.83,0:03:02.39,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Hah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.94,0:03:20.44,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan, if you don't properly go to school regularly, your attendance record will be really bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.44,0:03:23.07,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,You're slow, and your grades are poor{was: bad, changed to avoid repetition}.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.07,0:03:26.95,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,On top of being perverse, you don't have enough days in attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.95,0:03:31.28,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,It's like you're saying, "Let me repeat my second year."
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.28,0:03:34.46,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Then I might be in the same class as you next year.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.46,0:03:38.65,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I'm telling you to go to school on time so that it won't happen!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.65,0:03:41.28,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,I wouldn't go as far as telling you to stop publishing,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.28,0:03:44.09,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,but come to school more regularly.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.11,0:03:46.98,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I'll think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.98,0:03:49.15,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, think about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.72,0:03:53.88,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Say, have you been reading my manga lately?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.88,0:03:56.30,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I have.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.30,0:03:59.00,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You rarely tell me about your thoughts on them.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.00,0:04:02.86,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Because it's embarrassing to tell you what I think.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.86,0:04:07.10,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, even if I don't tell you, your readers write you letters, don't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.10,0:04:08.90,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Shindou Nagi-sensei.
