Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.90,0:04:10.97,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Don't call me that outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.97,0:04:12.82,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:14.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,No "Onii-chan" either.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.43,0:04:19.15,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Don't doze off.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.15,0:04:21.19,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Properly listen to what the teacher says.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.19,0:04:24.00,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,And if the teacher calls on you, answer clearly in a loud voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.00,0:04:26.01,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you my guardian?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.49,0:04:28.44,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,See you, Hirono-senpai.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.44,0:04:29.29,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.60,0:04:33.85,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You're unusually early, Hirono.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.85,0:04:35.15,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.15,0:04:37.44,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, you came to school with your girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.44,0:04:39.65,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I guess you've grown into more of a man.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.99,0:04:42.99,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,She's not my girlfriend, and it's none of your business.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.99,0:04:44.60,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Hirono.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.60,0:04:49.08,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Even if she's not your type, it's important to get along with the girl first.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.08,0:04:52.03,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Among her friends might be a girl that's your type.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.03,0:04:55.66,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,And there might be even more of your type among her friends' friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.66,0:05:00.14,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Your lack of discrimination towards girls is due to that strategy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.14,0:05:02.36,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I'm just a fickle person.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.36,0:05:05.35,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You think something said by someone like that would be persuasive?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.35,0:05:07.71,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,So, are you going to class today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:11.51,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Since I'm already here, I'll just go register my attendance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.51,0:05:13.33,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Attendance only?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.26,0:06:02.36,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.90,0:06:05.03,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,always...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.76,0:06:09.40,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,have a feeling of loss, as if I'm lacking something.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.84,0:06:14.89,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I always feel like a certain color is missing from the world I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.28,0:06:18.83,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,But I have no idea what color is missing,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.83,0:06:21.08,MainT,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,and the more I want to search for the answer, the further away I get.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.56,0:06:25.00,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Impatience is gnawing at my heart bit by bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.59,0:06:31.72,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're quite a reckless person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.09,0:06:34.72,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm an idiot, so I can only see what's in front of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.96,0:06:36.39,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,You're strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.39,0:06:38.03,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.03,0:06:42.96,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I just think that someone whose dream comes true has a kind of responsibility.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.96,0:06:45.48,Main,Yuko,0000,0000,0000,,Who would that responsibility be for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.51,0:06:52.33,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,For the dreamer, me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.67,0:06:59.72,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Did I fall asleep?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.42,0:07:02.54,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Are you awake, Hirono-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.07,0:07:04.04,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.04,0:07:07.23,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Morning. I'm Miyamura Miyako.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.23,0:07:10.17,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're a student at Otowa, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.17,0:07:12.68,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,My uniform looks pretty tempting too, doesn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.68,0:07:15.02,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You were totally asleep.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.02,0:07:17.60,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,If you sleep in a place like this, you'll catch a cold.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.60,0:07:19.55,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,So, why are you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.55,0:07:20.73,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Isn't it obvious?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.94,0:07:24.56,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I came to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.91,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs53\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:07:30.70,0:07:33.91,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The test is read backwards here, from right to left. It's a reference from the manga "Sayonara Zetsubou Sensei." 【さよなら絶望先生】
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.66,0:07:40.17,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,If only this car wasn't there, it would be a good shot.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.17,0:07:41.73,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Kyosuke.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.73,0:07:42.67,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.67,0:07:45.40,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The shots you took are good,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.40,0:07:47.46,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,but it's tough to combine them together.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.46,0:07:48.34,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.34,0:07:51.42,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,The shots require so much attention that they interrupt the flow.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.42,0:07:54.78,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,When I took the one-cuts, I put all my soul in it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.78,0:07:57.44,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,You should also give all you've got when editing.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.44,0:07:59.43,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,That kind of movie won't win.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.27,0:08:03.83,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to win at the Cinema Festival,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.83,0:08:06.99,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,you should cater to widely held interests.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.36,0:08:14.20,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,But--among our works--there are lots of fans who like the movies Kyosuke shoots.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.50,0:08:15.56,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,President?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.56,0:08:17.12,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Since those are popular,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.12,0:08:20.55,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,shouldn't our strategy be to make good use of Kyosuke's movies in our productions?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.55,0:08:22.87,Main,Guy,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.92,0:08:26.04,Main,Emi,0000,0000,0000,,Kyosuke?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.19,0:08:28.71,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to the bathroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.43,0:08:35.22,bw,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That's not it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:36.41,0:08:39.22,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,It's about time for me to retire.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.21,0:08:44.94,Main,Kyosuke,0000,0000,0000,,That girl... should be Hiro's...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.94,0:08:54.87,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's almost time for Renji-kun to come.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.87,0:08:57.45,MainT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to tell him the truth today.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.05,0:09:00.45,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.05,0:09:13.71,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Can I go to your place after my club activities, Onii-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.22,0:09:17.97,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, he has his deadline.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.92,0:09:24.16,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,But I was really surprised.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.16,0:09:26.98,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That you're in the same school as me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.98,0:09:29.98,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't come to school often.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.98,0:09:31.58,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.58,0:09:35.49,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,When it comes to school attendance, I'm known as the infamous, class-skipping devil.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.49,0:09:38.16,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's why we don't know each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.16,0:09:45.26,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,When I saw you, I was unsure whether I should call out to you or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.26,0:09:46.16,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.16,0:09:48.30,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I needed to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:48.30,0:09:50.46,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I'm a girl, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.46,0:09:51.88,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't understand at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.88,0:09:56.25,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,This is our reunion after just the two of us spent Christmas together.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.25,0:09:58.36,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,I want it to be romantic.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.36,0:10:02.00,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,We just spent our time in a karaoke bar and a family restaurant till morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.00,0:10:04.43,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Moreover, I paid for everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.43,0:10:06.43,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,By the way, Hirono-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.43,0:10:09.97,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry. To tell you the truth, I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.44,0:10:11.81,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,That note.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.52,0:10:16.67,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible you have that kind of dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.67,0:10:17.74,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.74,0:10:19.23,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be shy. Don't be shy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.23,0:10:21.30,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's not something embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.30,0:10:24.33,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,It's good to have a dream. Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.33,0:10:27.83,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than dreaming about it, I'm already a manga artist.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.83,0:10:29.67,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,A self-proclaimed one? Or an imaginary one?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.67,0:10:31.02,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,An active one.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.02,0:10:34.34,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,A professional one whose series appear in magazines.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.34,0:10:35.26,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.26,0:10:36.34,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.34,0:10:38.34,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,What kind of manga are you drawing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.34,0:10:41.11,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Generally speaking, shoujo manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.10,0:10:38.60,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\be1\move(352,-40,352,0,0,500)}A
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.10,0:10:38.60,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(352,-35,352,5,0,500)}Shoujo manga are intended to appeal to girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.60,0:10:46.70,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:10:38.60,0:10:46.70,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,Shoujo manga are intended to appeal to girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.70,0:10:47.26,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\be1\move(352,0,352,-40,0,500)}A
Dialogue: 1,0:10:46.70,0:10:47.26,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(352,5,352,-35,0,500)}Shoujo manga are intended to appeal to girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.11,0:10:42.09,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.09,0:10:47.26,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Now that you mention it, I see you have a girlish face.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:48.85,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's what you're surprised about?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.85,0:10:51.18,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Heh, that's amazing of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.18,0:10:54.61,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,In other words, you already have a job.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.61,0:10:55.75,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.75,0:10:57.67,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,You're already supporting yourself at such a young age.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.67,0:10:58.56,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.56,0:11:00.14,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,A dream life living on royalties...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.14,0:11:02.37,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Well... not that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.37,0:11:04.48,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Amazing. A master.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.48,0:11:06.35,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, shut up.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.35,0:11:10.92,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,If you have the time to praise others, try to do something to be praised for.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.92,0:11:12.43,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Wah, arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.43,0:11:14.20,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Take a look at my manga.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.20,0:11:16.75,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,There are plenty of lines in there that sound even more arrogant.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.75,0:11:18.76,Main,Miyako,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.76,0:11:20.09,Main,Hiro,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.77,0:11:55.63,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,From yesterday's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.16,0:11:58.71,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,To today's me...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.22,0:12:16.33,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.31,0:12:19.86,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro isn't here yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.78,0:12:46.97,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.97,0:12:50.48,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.48,0:12:51.72,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You're late today.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:58.93,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I was reading until after noon. Before I noticed... {literally she said "after noon", don't really know how else to put it -guu}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.93,0:13:00.22,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What were you reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.22,0:13:03.27,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, that's... how should I put it...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.13,0:13:05.61,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It was a boring book.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.01,0:13:08.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You were absorbed in a boring book?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.38,0:13:10.09,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, nah.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:10.09,0:13:11.77,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Rather than absorbed...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.77,0:13:13.73,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Something that you can't tell your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.73,0:13:15.81,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.81,0:13:18.28,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're my friend, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.28,0:13:19.00,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.69,0:13:21.88,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.92,0:13:24.27,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.27,0:13:29.26,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's okay for me to tell you, but please keep it a secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.26,0:13:30.30,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,No matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.43,0:13:32.81,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I won't tell anyone, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.97,0:13:37.67,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, a-actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.67,0:13:40.66,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't reading a story.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.66,0:13:42.41,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't reading?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.85,0:13:44.75,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Is it possible you were writing one?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.75,0:13:47.03,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're really mean.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.28,0:13:50.28,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Can you show it to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.28,0:13:52.43,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I refuse, no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.43,0:13:53.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.69,0:13:57.88,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But that's amazing. A story, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.88,0:14:00.01,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's a really unpleasant reaction. {hateful/unpleasant/whatever-u-deem-fit -guu}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.01,0:14:01.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what I meant.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.49,0:14:02.62,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Just slightly.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.62,0:14:04.64,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's a slightly unpleasant reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.64,0:14:08.11,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, I was just thinking of trying to write one too.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.11,0:14:10.16,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're writing one as well?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.16,0:14:11.53,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It was just a thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.53,0:14:14.41,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I received a career interest survey at school.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.41,0:14:16.68,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm thinking of becoming a novelist.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.68,0:14:18.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.51,0:14:21.04,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think that's a really good idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.04,0:14:21.99,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Honestly?{was: Really, changed to avoid repetition}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.99,0:14:22.93,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.93,0:14:27.10,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm interested to know what kind of story you'd write.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.10,0:14:29.32,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'm also interested to know what you wrote...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.32,0:14:30.95,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't worry about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.95,0:14:32.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.63,0:14:35.14,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You shouldn't touch it for the rest of your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.21,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Please keep it a secret even after you pass away or go to hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.21,0:14:39.41,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,O-Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.96,0:14:42.96,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Does that mean I'm going to hell?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.96,0:14:45.46,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But a career is hard to decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.46,0:14:47.04,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.04,0:14:48.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.38,0:14:51.47,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I think doing what you like will be the best choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.14,0:14:53.45,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.45,0:14:55.28,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I was told the same thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.28,0:14:57.03,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,By whom?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.03,0:14:57.97,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,An adult.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.47,0:15:01.25,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want to become?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.25,0:15:04.55,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I have a dream.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.55,0:15:05.42,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.94,0:15:10.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't want to become a novelist. I just want to write stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.57,0:15:14.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's just a single story, I want to complete one as my current self.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.57,0:15:15.75,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.75,0:15:17.84,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I believe you can do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.84,0:15:19.49,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.49,0:15:20.38,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.38,0:15:22.95,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Even though my guarantee is not reliable.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.95,0:15:24.70,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,That's not true.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.70,0:15:26.51,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you very much.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.51,0:15:29.13,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy about what you just said.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.27,0:15:36.61,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I have to start going to school again tomorrow. I don't want to go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.61,0:15:38.62,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You don't want to go?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.62,0:15:41.23,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not like I hate school though.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.99,0:15:43.85,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,School, eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.85,0:15:45.48,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.48,0:15:47.44,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.44,0:15:50.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's fun to hear about school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.31,0:15:52.10,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Rather, it's fun to hear because I can't go.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.10,0:15:53.06,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.06,0:15:57.01,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,My twin sister always tells me about her school.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.01,0:15:59.39,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If she sounds happy,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.94,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be happy after hearing it too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.94,0:16:02.80,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Twin?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.80,0:16:05.77,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Her personality is the complete opposite of mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.77,0:16:09.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan is like an animal that would die if it stops moving.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.25,0:16:13.11,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,She's a first-year student at Otowa.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.11,0:16:15.15,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Her name is Shindou Kei.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.09,0:16:19.01,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,But I won't run into her if she's in junior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.01,0:16:20.42,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,She's in senior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.42,0:16:20.99,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.99,0:16:22.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You two are twins, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.63,0:16:23.91,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.91,0:16:26.06,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, that means you're also...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:26.37,0:16:28.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If I went to school,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.05,0:16:30.03,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'd be a first-year student in senior high.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.03,0:16:32.53,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ah... I-I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.53,0:16:35.53,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Ack, I kept thinking she was younger than me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.91,0:16:39.28,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, should I call you "Shindou-san" from now on?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.01,0:16:41.79,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Chihiro" is fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:43.90,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone calls me that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.90,0:16:47.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Then can you call me "Renji?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.43,0:16:49.50,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"Asou-san" doesn't work?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.50,0:16:50.91,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It's not the correct form of address.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.91,0:16:53.40,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Then how about "Renji-san?"
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.40,0:16:56.28,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,"San" is embarrassing. Use "kun."
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.28,0:16:59.06,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll be the one who's embarrassed if I address you like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.06,0:17:01.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, see... as a friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.21,0:17:03.80,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.80,0:17:06.44,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'll call you "Renji-kun" from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.42,0:17:10.13,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun. Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.13,0:17:12.82,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun. Renji-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.31,0:17:17.75,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.11,0:17:15.78,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It feels weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.39,0:17:19.39,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:17:17.39,0:17:19.39,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The furigana next to it says "Yakusoku", which means "Promise."
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.61,0:17:24.33,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.33,0:17:25.89,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.89,0:17:26.79,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,See you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.79,0:17:28.83,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.84,0:17:33.21,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:36.68,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.91,0:17:39.30,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I... I...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.30,0:17:40.47,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.47,0:17:44.85,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Nah, it's nothing. Goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.28,0:17:46.14,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.14,0:17:47.23,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.23,0:17:48.33,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.65,0:17:49.77,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.77,0:17:51.33,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Let's have fun again tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.33,0:17:54.03,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I'll come to the station after school.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.03,0:17:56.79,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Can you make it tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.03,0:17:58.49,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I think so.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.12,0:18:01.74,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Okay. I'll see you at the station tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.21,0:18:07.62,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,So it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.85,0:18:10.88,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,The one she met.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.14,0:18:12.46,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Himura-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.46,0:18:16.83,Main,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,If you want to stay by Chihiro's side, you have to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:24.81,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-san...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.16,0:18:28.43,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Renji-kun said to me, "Let's have fun tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.43,0:18:30.81,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just a greeting like "see you".
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.81,0:18:33.32,bwT,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's a real promise this time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.65,0:18:35.44,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,"See you tomorrow."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.95,0:18:43.64,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Onee-chan,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.64,0:18:48.03,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I can't imagine "tomorrow" and "happiness."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.03,0:18:49.22,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Will I...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.22,0:18:52.58,bw,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Will I still be here tomorrow?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.58,0:18:56.67,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs36\be1}A
Dialogue: 1,0:18:52.58,0:18:56.67,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,The story he's reading is a folktale called "Kachikachi Yama." 【かちかち山】
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.24,0:19:01.64,MainF,Yu,0000,0000,0000,,{\1c&HEFEFF2&\3c&HEFEFF2&\4c&HEFEFF2&\t(22,355,\1c&HF1DED4&\3c&H2B0806&\4c&H2B0806&)}If you want to stay by Chihiro's side, you have to be prepared.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.01,0:19:06.56,MainT,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't say "be prepared," or something like that, under normal circumstances.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.74,0:19:35.88,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yahoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.97,0:19:40.72,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Are you Renji-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.39,0:19:42.47,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.47,0:19:44.00,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.03,0:19:45.25,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Good afternoon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.71,0:19:47.43,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,What should we do today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.43,0:19:49.12,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go shopping somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.12,0:19:51.41,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a place with only a few people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.98,0:19:56.36,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I don't like going outside or to places with a lot of people.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.86,0:20:01.82,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,It's really beautiful.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.82,0:20:04.24,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. As if it's burning.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.05,0:20:06.63,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Asou Renji-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.63,0:20:07.37,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.37,0:20:10.90,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Am I your friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.93,0:20:13.34,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you asking me again?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.34,0:20:16.15,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe it doesn't mean anything particularly special to you. {I'm not sure what he means either. the term "friend", or the question itself? -guu}
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.15,0:20:20.32,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,What am I to you, then?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.32,0:20:22.77,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I think I was interested in you from the start.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.77,0:20:25.06,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,And then, before long, I couldn't leave you alone, or rather...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.06,0:20:27.55,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I'm not worried about you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.55,0:20:29.27,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,I always want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.27,0:20:31.70,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Like a sister?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:31.70,0:20:33.98,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,It does feel like a sister too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.98,0:20:38.68,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I also thought that if I had an elder brother, it would be someone like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.68,0:20:39.47,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.47,0:20:40.34,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.83,0:20:42.68,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,And, erm...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.68,0:20:44.11,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.11,0:20:45.21,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Chihiro.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.21,0:20:46.05,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.05,0:20:47.23,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Take a deep breath.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.14,0:20:52.83,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Write "person" on your palm, and then pretend to eat it.
