Dialogue: 1,0:20:48.40,0:20:52.57,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,This is a popular practice in Japan that is supposed to help a nervous person calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:53.07,Notes Box,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\fs53\be1\move(352,0,352,-60,0,500)}A
Dialogue: 1,0:20:52.57,0:20:53.07,Notes,TL Note,0000,0000,0000,,{\move(352,5,352,-55,0,500)}This is a popular practice in Japan that is supposed to help a nervous person calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.47,0:20:54.46,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.80,0:20:59.29,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry, I was testing you a little.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.06,0:21:05.25,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I wasn't sure emotionally if you were the right one to talk to about this,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:05.25,0:21:06.92,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,but now I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.92,0:21:11.03,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't change before, and now.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.39,0:21:14.63,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Erm, you're not a different person, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.63,0:21:15.56,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Eh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.56,0:21:18.07,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Well, since you have a twin sister,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.07,0:21:21.60,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,you're not going to tell me that you switched places with your elder sister, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.60,0:21:23.31,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.31,0:21:26.81,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I can't help being regarded as a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.29,0:21:29.57,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Asou-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.08,0:21:35.82,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I have a memory defect.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:38.59,Main,Renji,0000,0000,0000,,Memory... defect?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.59,0:21:39.60,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.60,0:21:43.59,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,My memory doesn't last longer than thirteen hours.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.85,0:21:49.47,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,In that sense, yesterday's me and today's me are two different people.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.85,0:21:53.43,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,Even if I live past today, I won't become tomorrow's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.43,0:21:55.95,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,I've always been like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.27,0:21:58.55,Main,Chihiro,0000,0000,0000,,And I will always be like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:35.83,0:23:39.07,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,My feelings and that person's feelings pass by each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.48,0:23:44.13,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode, ef - a tale of memories: Paradox.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.73,0:23:47.52,Main,Kei,0000,0000,0000,,Do you have memories you don't want to forget?
